# Canonical first-party error codes — the build-time stability lock (ADR-0024 D5-5).
# Sorted, one <domain>.<symbol> per line. The ErrorCodeGatesTest diffs the scanned codes
# against this file. Adding a code = append it here in the same change set; renaming or
# removing one = a breaking change to an external contract (review + major version).
# @Deprecated codes stay listed as tombstones until intentionally retired.
cli.artifact-exists
cli.kind-dir-mismatch
cli.resource-not-found
cli.unknown-connector
dsl.ambiguous-reference
dsl.composition
dsl.config-type-mismatch
dsl.duplicate-id
dsl.forbidden-field
dsl.illegal-expression
dsl.illegal-value
dsl.invalid-config-value
dsl.malformed-yaml
dsl.missing-reference
dsl.mode-mismatch
dsl.unknown-field
dsl.unsupported-mode
lifecycle.illegal-transition
role.unsupported
